SUMMARY:Georgios Papadopoulos Γεώργιος Παπαδόπουλος (King’s College London), Scale and conformal invariance in 2‐dimensional sigma models
DESCRIPTION:I shall demonstrate that all scale invariant two‐dimensional sigma models with compact target space are conformally invariant. The proof relies on techniques developed by Perelman for the proof of the Poincaré conjecture that I shall review.
UID:GeorgiosPapadopoulosΓεώργιοςΠαπαδόπουλος20250312@hertsmathphys.github.io
