SUMMARY:Charles Strickland‐Constable (University of Hertfordshire), Generalised geodesics: the geometry of strings and branes
DESCRIPTION:I will present recent work showing how the classical solutions of string and membrane sigma models can be understood as the analogue of integral curves of auto‐parallel vector fields in generalised geometry.I will try to make the first part of the talk accessible to a non‐string‐theory audience.
