SUMMARY:Ben Gripaios (University of Cambridge), Varieties of gauge theories
DESCRIPTION:I will describe the use of methods of arithmetic geometry to find gauge theories in 4 dimensions that are free of anomalies. In many cases, it is possible to find all such theories.
UID:BenGripaios20251126@hertsmathphys.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260413T162346Z
